{
  "stem": "1141.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they all con-- they all congregated in Mukacevo, in a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All the people from around-- Mukacevo was a big city, and all the people from around the area was congregated.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was a-- outside the city, it was a lumber yard, and they made-- the military used to be there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They cleared out, and they put all these people in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whole families, everybody was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] little by little, they started emptying them out and put them in the cattle trains and take them to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The warning signals were, the-- the people were bewildered.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They didn't know what was happening because something like this-- nobody anticipated that something like this can happen.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were rumors going around that they were taking people into Germany to work-- to work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But nobody ever knew [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the consequences.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody anticipated that there are crama-- crematoriums and concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The rumors went around that we are going to go to work, to Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the rumors were spread by the German Gestapo so the people wouldn't try to fight back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And so we went along.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whatever we were told to do, we did it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The worst part-- we were in that ghetto and the food was scarce.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were with buses, with-- with-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not donkeys.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What do you call these wagons where they have-- every possible way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By buses, by train, whichever way they-- they transported us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On trucks.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The worst part of it, what I will never forget as long-- as long as I live, my youngest brother [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] was in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
